HOW TO USE:
Parameters:
	inputfile	--	path to original file with extension 
	budget		--	[debug, rc, rcg]
	dimension	--	dimension in number for generate output file 
	platform	--	[ios, android]
	outputfile	--	path to outpuf file with extension

Example:

$ ./applybadge.sh pathToInputFile.png rcg 180 ios pathToOutputFile.png
$ ./applybadge.sh pathToInputFile.png debug 192 android pathToOutputFile.png